window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>On January 1st, 2020, the comet hit, and a good chunk of the people on Earth died or turned into mutants.</p> <p>But some people gained powerful magical abilities.</p> <p>You would think that the fall of humankind would usher in a time of peace and happiness for the survivors, but since powerful people tend to be assholes, life got worse, and these mages enslaved those who couldnâ€™t protect themselves.</p> <p>I have magic too, but not just any magic.</p> <p>I can summon guns, and nothing kills asshole mages better than a bullet through the brain.</p> <p>Disclaimer: This is a slow-burn harem series with explicit sex scenes.</p>"; 
